    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a recent comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut, supported by OEM-spec suspension and a factory limited-slip differential. Every panel retains original paint with zero oxidation, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear. A true turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
