    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating; you will find zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather seats remain supple with no visible bolsters wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the driver-assist systems to the infotainment, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has never seen a winter, never been through an automated car wash, and has been driven only on fair-weather weekends. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than the best. Includes all original manuals, two keys, and the original window sticker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
